E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1540','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-04/2c723428f466cba149588d59c465a5ec.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">检查东湖围堤<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>日，市长任振鹤，市人大常委会副主任胡毓军，副市长闫英姿一行来嘉鱼县检查防汛备汛工作。市政府秘书长夏福卿，县领导熊征宇、余珂、李国光、李鹏谋、葛婷、魏萍陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">市领导一行先后来到渡普镇东湖围堤茅花咀段、洲湾百里长渠、洲湾河埠崩岸险段、余码头泵站、余码头大闸等地进行了实地查看，了解各处整险加固、泵站机器运行情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据介绍，我县于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2010</span>年底投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">292</span>万元对东湖围堤进行了重点整治，堤面加宽至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>&mdash;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>米，堤顶加高至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>&mdash;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>米，防洪能力有所提高。洲湾百里长渠清淤工程已完成，汛期通畅排水得到保障。余码头泵站已完成维修与保养，目前该泵站<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>台机组已开机灌溉。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">任振鹤要求，要从思想上、认识上、预案上和组织上，做好防汛防洪抗旱各项准备工作。在认识上要做好有灾准备，组织上抓好落实，预案上抓好保障，各项责任要尽快上肩。要做好各项防汛隐患的排查工作，要高度重视江段、干堤和崩岸险段，积极向上争取长江干堤的除险加固。要高度重视湖堤整治工作，抓好泵站的维修检测，加大涵闸维护力度。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">任振鹤强调，要做好汛期内的科学调度工作。市县要加强衔接，做好江湖河库潮的科学调度，做到宁早不得迟，能排不等天。要做好防汛防洪抗旱各项基础工作，做到渠道要顺畅、泵站要待机，涵闸要能启，道路要畅通，同时要加快防汛抢险物资储备，确保安全度汛。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇表示，为切实做好今年防汛抗旱的各项工作，我县将把防汛责任、汛前检查、物料准备、汛期调度、应急预案落实到位，进一步在思想上保持高度警惕，加强对各水利设施的检查，督促做好水利工程煞尾和隐患工程的整改工作；全面落实防汛队伍，备齐备足防汛物料，确保安全渡汛。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，自今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月份以来，县委、县政府领导带队先后对辖区水利设施和在建水利工程、水情测报点及堤段备料库开展了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>次汛前检查。目前长江干堤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">56.6</span>公里和洲湾堤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">41</span>公里堤顶尚好，沿江涵闸、穿堤建筑物未发现异常现场。全县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>处民堤民垸和东、西湖围堤经过两年的整治，防洪能力得到提高。全县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19</span>座大中小型水库状态良好，水库大坝公路畅通，输水管完好，溢洪道畅通。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>处水雨观测站设施已完成维护与保养，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日各测报站投入正常测报。全县已储备草袋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.1</span>万条，编织袋<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">35</span>万条，彩条布<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.9</span>万米，铁丝<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.5</span>吨，救生衣<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">270</span>件等防汛物资。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-04/d64c836ab84e6a9bbba708e590d9f2e9.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">查看防洪形势图</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1541','6','熊铁山、卢妮','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-04/03e4ada9b90102c92b0fffb9997609f4.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>日，全县中小企业成长工程推进工作会召开。县委副书记李国光，副县长许隆高出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李国光指出，中小企业不仅是县域经济的基础和平台，关系着县域经济排序，更是推动经济社会发展的重要力量，在繁荣经济、增加就业、推动创新、催生产业、扩大内需等方面发挥着重要作用。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李国光要求，各级各部门要加强中小企业成长工程的培养力度，发展是硬道理，只有中小企业迅速发展起来了，中小企业的申报工作才能更好的开展起来；要加强中小企业申报工作的业务培训和业务指导，要让各级申报工作人员有科学的态度，钉子的精神和适应新形势的能力；要加强中小企业成长工程申报的领导工作，要一把手亲自抓，分管领导重点抓，明确目标责任；要成立督办小组和工作专班，加强中小企业成长工程的对接和督办工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">许隆高要求，各部门要认清形势、正视问题、鼓足干劲、振奋精神，转变作风，调动一切积极因素，汇聚攻坚克难的强大合力，按时办结，保质保量完成全年目标任务。经贸局和统计局要进行分工，搞责任制，确保申报工作分工落实到位；各个乡镇把工作具体到人，哪个地方出现了问题，就对负责人进行问责。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">经信局局长朱明凤通报了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年全县工业成长过程存在的问题并将近期申报工作任务及全年工作的推进做了安排。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">统计局局长孙昌勇通报了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年工业成长工程的统计情况，并就下一步工业统计工作做了安排。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">各镇及经济开发区就工业成长工程的申报、整改及完成全年目标任务情况做了汇报。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，一季度，全县工业总产值完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">65.36</span>亿元，同比增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">38.77%</span>，增幅居全市第二位；完成工业增加值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18.5</span>亿元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>同比增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21.9%</span>；规模工业企业上缴税金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5883.8</span>万元<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">,</span>同比增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">23.96%</span>；地方一般财政预算收入完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.6</span>亿元，同比增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">33.9%</span>；全社会固定资产投资完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17.01</span>亿元，同比增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">53.6%</span>；顺利实现全县经济一季度&ldquo;开门红&rdquo;。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-04/79e489b05a2823b3b1b3780b1626b4f6.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1542','6','张姝、李妮','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-04/80cf60015e1ca45f61d82962549a65da.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">捐赠活动现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">捧着叔叔阿姨送来的爱心字典和图书，每位孩子脸上都露出灿烂的笑容。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，市纪委、市住建委向嘉鱼县新街镇马鞍山村和晒甲山村捐赠了价值一万余元的电脑和图书。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\