ght: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1544','6','刘蒙、张伟','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0505/20120505010217997.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0505/20120505101038457.jpg\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p>图为会议现场</o:p></span></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"4\\\\\" month=\\\\\"5\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>日下午</st1:chsdate>，我县召开优秀年轻干部座谈会。县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记、县长余珂与全县年轻干部代表共聚一堂，交心谈心，了解他们工作的体会，听取他们对我县加强培养年轻干部的建议。县委副书记李国光，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">当天，来自各镇和县直单位的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">23</span>名<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>岁以下的正股级、副科级、正科级年轻干部代表参加会议。他们结合自身的工作岗位，畅谈心得体会，交流工作经验，分享成长喜悦，并对我县进一步加强对年轻干部的培养提出了许多建设性的看法。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">熊征宇指出，优秀年轻干部就是财富，关系到我县各项事业的发展，各级各部门要高度重视年轻干部的成长和发展。他说，培养年轻干部重在党性锻炼和能力提升，广大年轻干部们既要坚定理想信念，又要坚定磨练的意志；既要志存高远，又要脚踏实地；既要富有激情，又要淡定执着；既要注重组织培养，又要注重自身实践。他强调，年轻干部要充分发扬年轻人特有的优势，克服年轻人固有的不足，紧密结合嘉鱼实际，紧跟嘉鱼发展脉搏，尽职尽责做好本职工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">熊征宇表示，下一步我县将组织实施年轻干部成长工程，这既是对省委、市委重视年轻干部培养重要精神的贯彻，也是我县各项事业发展的迫切需要。他要求，组织部门要解放思想，创新思路，破除平衡照顾、求全责备、以偏概全的思想，要在工作、生活、情感等方面全方位地对年轻干部给予关心，加快他们茁壮成长。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">余珂在座谈会上用 &ldquo;唯有源头活水来&rdquo;、&ldquo;天生我材必有用&rdquo;、&ldquo;千磨万砺还坚劲&rdquo;、&ldquo;纸上得来终觉浅&rdquo;、&ldquo;吹尽黄沙始见金&rdquo;五句诗词来勉励年轻干部，鼓励他们要善于学习，在工作中始终保持进取心；要坚持不懈，克服各种挫折，勇敢面对困难；要重视实践，深入基层，学会与群众打交道；要铭记责任和使命感，实现自己的理想，体现自己的人生价值。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1545','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-06/bf8934c1f785d72f003d2af49602e8d3.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"4\\\\\" month=\\\\\"5\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>日</st1:chsdate>，嘉鱼县政法委召开全县政法系统&ldquo;双百双联&rdquo;主题实践活动动员大会。县委常委、政法委书记朱从钦出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据悉，全县政法机关将与百家企业、百个村居开展结队共建活动。政法系统的领导干部、广大干警将走出机关，深入车间班组、田间地头，帮助解决生产、生活中的困难问题；开展法制教育，化解矛盾纠纷，在全县政法系统掀起了&ldquo;零障碍、零容忍、零阻力、零干扰、零距离、零投诉、零拖延，心贴心、面对面&rdquo;服务的热潮。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">为确保这项活动有序进行、取得实效，县政法委在广泛征求意见的基础上，研究制定了主题实践活动实施方案，成立了领导小组。政法部门正股职以上干部将每人联系一个企业（项目）、一个村（社区），联系对象三年不变。联系企业干警，每月至少到所联系企业开展实地走访、调研一次，并作好记录，每季度将联系活动形成书面材料归档；联系村（社区）干警，每周至少到联系点开展一次民情调查，及时掌握社情民意，帮助化解矛盾纠纷，每月将联系点的情况形成书面材料归档。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据透露，政法干警&ldquo;双百双联&rdquo;主题实践活动情况将纳入业绩档案，作为政法干警提拔使用考核依据。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-06/b3205993bf93758c180f753460bf6e28.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1546','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，在嘉鱼洁丽雅二期建设项目现场，推土机、运输车辆来回穿梭，近</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">名施工人员正有条不紊地忙碌着。该项目计划投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，目前已完成年产</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万吨特种纱生产线、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1.5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万吨毛巾生产线厂房和办公楼主体建筑。在现场的企业负责人介绍说：&ldquo;项目之所以能够快速推进，得益于县里的&lsquo;一线工作法&rsquo;&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">今年是项目建设年，我县共有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多个续建、在建项目。为推进项目建设，嘉鱼大力推行&ldquo;一线工作法&rdquo;，领导在一线指挥，工作在一线推开，问题在一线解决。我县成立了<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">嘉鱼</span>长江大桥、咸嘉新城等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重大项目前期推进领导小组，组建了经济开发区二期、<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">嘉鱼</span>大道等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重点项目建设指挥部，对全县涉及工业、农业、旅游、交通等领域的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">56</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重点项目，分别明确了第一责任单位，落实了县级领导联点责任。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为全面优化环境，促使项目快速、顺利推进，我县结合&ldquo;<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">百日环境大整治</span>&rdquo;活动，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">清理</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">现有审批事项，优化审批流程，严格落实&ldquo;一卡制&rdquo;收费；为重大项目、重点企业开辟&ldquo;绿色通道&rdquo;，大力推行无偿代办制、首问负责制、服务承诺制、限时办结制等制度。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">全县政法部门开展&ldquo;百名干警联百家企业&rdquo;，为项目推进保驾护航。以政法委机关和公检法司部门的干部为联络员，确定对口联系企业、联系基层。联络员至少每月到对口联系点走访一次，及时帮企业解决周边治安整治、企业内部治安防范、行政审批&ldquo;绿色通道&rdquo;等问题，实现环境&ldquo;零干扰&rdquo;、管理&ldquo;零事故&rdquo;、服务&ldquo;零距离&rdquo;。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">基层是大课堂，一线是大舞台。我县选调综合素质高、发展潜力大的优秀干部到重点工程项目建设一线进行锻炼。将干部参与重点工程项目情况作为考核选拔干部的重要内容，树立起&ldquo;能力在一线培养、业绩在一线考核、用人在一线选拔&rdquo;的导向。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;一线工作法&rdquo;如同发展的风向标，讲实干、重实效，成为全县上下的共识。广大干部自觉抵制&ldquo;庸&rdquo;、&ldquo;懒&rdquo;、&ldquo;散&rdquo;等不良作风，深入基层一线，转作风、提效能、抓落实、促发展，影响和带动全县群众干事创业，掀起新一轮发展热潮。截至</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月底，全县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">56</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重点项目已开工在建</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">38</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，累计完成投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元。第一季度，全县规模以上工业企业完成总产值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">65.36</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">38.77</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">％；实现工业增加值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">18.49</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，入库税金达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5883.8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1547','288','程雨','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/jianshehubeijingjiqiangxianzhongdianxiangmujianshezhuanti/2012-05-09/e6f7a3c9675212048a62408162eca1dc.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">图为项目施工现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>日，天朗气清，正是室外施工好时机。在官桥镇石鼓岭村的大连成达项目建设基地上，挖掘机、铲土机、大型卡车共计<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>余台，正在工地上来回穿梭、加班加点作业。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">该项目责任领导、县委副书记李国光于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日晚在该镇主要负责人的陪同下来到施工场地慰问工作人员，详细了解项目建设情况。他充分肯定了该镇在项目施工中&ldquo;抢晴天、战雨天&rdquo;的做法，同时嘱咐施工单位要在保证施工质量和安全的前提下，加快建设进度。镇相关部门则要明确目标责任，及时帮助解决项目在推进过程中遇到的问题，力促项目早建成、早投产、早达效。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">自<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>月份以来，官桥镇严格按照县委、县政府关于加快项目建设的有关要求，该镇坚持&ldquo;四个突出&rdquo;：即突出解放思想转观念、、突出优化分解强责任、突出抢先争优促进度、突出科学管理保质量，树立&ldquo;坚持工业第一战略，突出项目第一抓手&rdquo;宗旨，严格掌控涉及官桥镇的重点项目建设进度。发扬<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>五加二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>白加黑<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>的实干精神，坚持晴天大干、雨天创造条件干，全面加速项目建设步伐。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">据悉，大连成达加工项目总投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>亿元，其中工业园区建设面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>亩，主要建设集规模化养殖基地、禽类屠宰加工、冷冻、销售、食品加工生产及饲料加工、养殖加工及生活服务区为一体的综合项目。第一期固定资产投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>亿元，建设周期<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>个月，主要建设肉鸡屠宰加工厂及万吨冷库与<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">130</span>个现代化肉鸡养殖小区。目前，第一期土方平整工程已完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>万方，实现完成工程总量的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1/3</span>，预计在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>个有效工作日内可全部完成土地平整任务。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1548','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-09/f2dac9b6612b3a05ad658f3f7da21313.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">在葛洲坝水泥采石场检查<br />\r\n</font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-09/2609d81b4b1cca893e6e0fa224991c06.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">在白云山采石场检查</font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">9</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，由市国土局副局长田时学带队的市政府安全生产矿山专项检查组赴嘉鱼县，检查我县非煤矿山安全监管工作。检查组一行实地检查了葛洲坝水泥采石场、白云山采石场等地，并听取了情况汇报。副县长饶自斌出席汇报会。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据介绍，我县目前有非煤矿山企业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">17</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家，其中黄金开采</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家、石灰岩开采</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">13</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家、大理石开采</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家、锰矿开采</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家。开采方式均为露天开采。有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家在</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年安全生产标准化创建活动中达标，其中</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家达二级，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家达三级。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">今年以来，我县切实抓好非煤矿山安全监管工作，消除各类事故隐患，杜绝重特大事故发生。对不符合安全生产条件的矿山一律停产整顿，严把复工验收质量关。在安全投入上，要求足额缴纳安全生产风险抵押金，为职工交投保额为</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元的安全生产责任险。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">我县深入开展&ldquo;打非治违&rdquo;和企业自查专项行动，杜绝非法违法生产行为，同时加强日常监管和服务，建立健全长效机制。今年</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月，我县对</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家采矿许可证到期没有办理延期手续的企业，提前</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">天暂扣了其安全生产许可证，并责令停产，直到其按要求办理了采矿许可证延期手续才恢复其生产。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">检查组充分肯定了我县非煤矿山安全监管工作，认为我县做到了领导高度重视、责任主体明确、工作机制健全、协调督办到位，在安全监管上取得了良好的成效。检查组要求我县在下一步工作中，坚持预防为主，着力排查治理隐患，做到严格细致、不留死角，并实现企业日常安全管理常态化。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县政府办副主任刘军、县安监局局长骆名奇陪同检查。</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-09/3327e992ce51852a4942e2f8cbea0729.jpg\\\\\" /></font></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">汇报会现场</font></div>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1549','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-09/324a81e9066b74f9d6abb165efbcade7.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><br />\r\n<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-09/885606216cd27472f79f24f5e65bffdd.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n颁奖仪式现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"5\\\\\" day=\\\\\"9\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">9</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，嘉鱼县总工会召开十一届五次全委（扩大）会议，总结成绩，表彰先进，安排部署下一阶段工作任务。县委常委、统战部长、县总工会主席李新华出席会议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议指出，去年，全县各级工会围绕加快发展、服务发展的理念，强化机关&ldquo;四位一体&rdquo;（困难职工帮扶中心、职工法律援助中心、农民工维权服务中心、劳动争议调解中心）帮扶工作体系建设，深入开展困难职工摸底调查，建有困难职工档案</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多户，涉及职工</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多人。同时，各级工会通过组织开展寒冬送温暖、盛夏送清凉、金秋助学、看望劳模等一系列关爱行动，累计发放慰问帮扶资金</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余万元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，全县工会将进一步深化&ldquo;两大工程&rdquo;，即职工建功立业工程和维权机制社会化建设工程。同时，还将努力办好&ldquo;六件实事&rdquo;，即筹集</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元开展&ldquo;送清凉&rdquo;、&ldquo;送温暖&rdquo;活动；为</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">40</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">名困难职工子女上大学提供资助；组建嘉鱼县职工艺术团，开展为一线职工送文化活动；组织</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">名劳模、农民工疗休养；组织</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人参加职工医疗互助活动；联合有关方面，做好农民工技能培训、职业介绍、家政培训。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议对</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多家工会工作先进单位和</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多名先进个人进行了表彰。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">十一届工会委员会委员、各镇工会主席、县直各部门工会主席、部分企业工会主席及人数较多单位的女工主任参加会议。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-09/e66ab568f216cd9bf060d4d67157f563.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议现场</font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1550','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-10/b8793257a4f803e8dadf6bc5f08f2937.jpg\\\\\" />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">检查登记表</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-05-10/6339c2be10cfe73d9f3d921b9fdb05f3.jpg\\\\\" />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">检查</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超室</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>日下午，省人大常委会委员、教科文卫委员会副主任委员袁军晶带队的省人大调研组，来我县检查指导综合治理出生人口性别比工作。市人大常委会副主任程学娟，县领导余珂、李国光、葛婷、刘合权、李电波、魏萍等陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">调研组一行来到我县官桥镇卫生院，查看了该院<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">B</span>超检查室，翻阅了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">B</span>超检查登记表等资料。据了解，官桥镇卫生院在实施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">B</span>超孕检时，都必须实行实名登记，规范填写&ldquo;孕妇超生诊断仪检测登记表&rdquo;，包括检查日期、姓名、出生年月、婚姻状况、现有女子、妊娠时间、身份证号、详细家庭住址等内容，在确认真实身份后，医生要详细、准确、完整地做好<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">B</span>超登记记录，并将这些信息在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时内录入共享平台。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">下一步，调研组还将对我县人民医院计划生育实名登记及&ldquo;两禁两非&rdquo;相关工作进行检查，并听取我县综合治理出生人口性别比工作情况的汇报。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1551','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]45</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: .5gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: .5gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">经县人民政府同意，现将《嘉鱼县城乡劳动者自主创业小额贷款担保基金管理办法》印发给你们，请认真遵照执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 231pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 16.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0</span>一二年四月二十六日<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉鱼县城乡劳动者自主创业小额贷款担保基金管理办法<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第一章 总 则<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 35pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第一条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>为解决我县城乡劳动者自谋职业、自主创业过程中小额担保贷款问题，根据鄂政发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2008]60</span>号、鄂财社规<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2011]19</span>号文件的规定，结合本县实际情况，特制订本办法。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第二条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>本办法所称小额贷款担保，是指由嘉鱼县下岗失业人员小额贷款担保服务中心（以下简称担保服务中心），根据合同约定，以保证的方式为城乡劳动者自主创业担保贷款提供担保，保证贷款银行债权实现的法律行为。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第三条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>本办法遵循《中华人民共和国担保法》规定的平等、自愿、公平、诚实守信原则，通过科学的风险管理机制，保障合同当事人各方的合法权益。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第二章 贷款担保资金来源与规模<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第四条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> 嘉鱼县城乡劳动者自主创业小额贷款担保基金（以下简称担保基金）由嘉鱼县财政局筹集和管理，专项用于促进嘉鱼县城乡劳动者自谋职业和自主创业。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第五条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> 担保基金的筹集额度按与城乡劳动者自主创业的实际需求相适应的规模安排，并按照担保基金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3-5</span>倍的规模发放贷款。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第三章 贷款担保管理机构<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第六条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>设立担保基金监督管理委员会（以下简称监管会）；监管会下设担保服务中心。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第七条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>监管会由嘉鱼县财政局、人民银行嘉鱼县支行、嘉鱼县人力资源和社会保障局、嘉鱼县工商行政管理局、嘉鱼县妇女联合会、金融经办机构和担保服务中心组成，每半年召开一次监管会会议，或经监管会成员提议召开临时监管会会议。主要职责为：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）审议小额贷款担保业务年度工作计划和工作报告；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）审议、批准弥补代偿损失方案；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）审议、核销坏帐；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）经批准调整担保基金规模。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第八条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> 担保服务中心为担保基金的日常管理机构。主要职责为：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）执行经监管会审议的年度工作计划，组织实施监管会决议；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）对监管会负责，于每年一季度报告上年度工作情况及本年度工作计划；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）负责担保基金日常管理；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）向监管会提交核销坏帐、弥补代偿损失的方案；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）提交担保基金调整规模的方案；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（六）监管会交办的其他工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第四章 贷款担保对象和条件<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第九条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>担保基金具体提供担保的对象和条件为：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）具有本县城乡居民户口，男<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>岁、女<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">55</span>岁以下，身体健康，诚实守信，本地创业人员经工商管理部门批准领取了营业执照，自谋职业、自主创业从事个体经营的城乡劳动者；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）符合上述条件的城乡劳动者自主创业合伙经营和组织起来就业创办的劳动密集型小企业，其吸纳就业困难人员不得低于企业人员总数的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30%</span>；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）对符合上述条件，新办个体经营、劳动密集小企业的城乡劳动者自主创业的小额贷款项目，国家限制行业除外，现有微利项目，原则上予以优先重点扶持；<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）城乡劳动者自主创业申请担保贷款时，必须合法经营，资信程度良好，有偿还能力且必须在贷款发放银行开立帐户。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第五章 贷款担保额度、期限与用途<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第十条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>贷款担保额度：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）对单个自然人自谋职业、自主创业的，贷款金额不超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>万元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）对城乡劳动者自主创业合伙经营或组织起来就业、创办小企业的，可按每人不超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>万元，总额不超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>万元的额度实行&ldquo;捆绑式贷款&rdquo;。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）对符合条件的劳动密集型小企业，贷款额度不超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>万元。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第十一条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>贷款担保期限一般为一年，最长不超过二年。借款人提出展期的，在确定借款人展期期限内能够及时履行债务的前提下，担保服务中心同意继续提供担保的，金融经办机构展期一次，展期期限不得超过一年。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第十二条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>还款方式按金融经办机构有关规定执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第十三条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>借款人应将贷款用作自谋职业、自主创业或合伙经营和组织起来就业创办小企业的流动资金。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第六章 贷款担保程序<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 35pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">第十四条</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> <span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span>需要提供小额贷款担保的城乡劳动者，按照自愿申请、社区受理评审后择优推荐、经劳动就业管理局审核、担保服务中心复核并出具承诺担保书、金融经办机构核贷的程序，办理贷款手续。上述部门应在规定时间内完成各自办事程序。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 